Author-Name: Ehrlich, Clifford J.
Abstract: A tidal wave of change is sweeping across the American workplace. Resulting in part from tumultuous economic conditions, the relationship between employers and employees is being redefined in a fundamental and permanent way. The consequences are as critical to the future of business as are developments in marketing, financial management, and technology.
